config.script:
logger = system.util.getLogger('removeActiveCall')
	
	try:
		tagPath = self.session.custom.EqPath
		reasonID = self.view.custom.SelectedReason
		notes = self.view.custom.SelectedNotes
		modeEventID = self.view.custom.EventID
		userName = self.session.custom.UserName
		stateEventSubID = self.parent.parent.getChild("SubReason/Dropdown").props.value
		stateEventFinalID = reasonID
		
		if self.parent.parent.getChild("SubReason/Dropdown").props.enabled:
			stateEventFinalID = stateEventSubID
		
		if reasonID != '' and notes != '':
			res = mes.downtime.sp.upsertEventCallsReason(modeEventID, stateEventFinalID, userName, notes)
			system.perspective.print(res)
			if res is not True: raise ValueError('Sproc call failed.')
			
			mes.oee.mode.setModeProduction(tagPath)
			system.perspective.sendMessage('productionChange')
			system.perspective.closePopup('activeCall')
		else:
			raise ValueError("One or more fields is empty.")
	except Exception as e:
		gpa.frontEnd.localUI.throwError(str(e))
